Reproducibility
---------------

This repository pins versions in pyproject.toml [project.dependencies] and the
lock files `pixi.lock` and `uv.lock`. The bounds are intentionally narrow and
deliberately mirror Hephaestus's floor/upper-cap policy to keep CI, myrmidon,
and pip-install environments on the same major versions.

